{
  "stem": "25835.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Each day we received piece of bread, about 200, as I said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every second day, piece of margarine, which was maybe 2 millimeters thick, and 1 by 1 inch big.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once a week, one teaspoon of sugar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every day, one cup of very thin soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you find-- found one piece of potato, you, you were [LAUGHS] very happy, but mostly from leaves of beets.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one time, ersatz soup-- ersatz coffee-- you know what that is, 'ersatz.' And that's it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this-- I was so happy, unfortunately, that my, my mother divide own portion for three.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She gave us one third of portion, therefore, maybe I'm-- I could survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But she lost lot of weight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From, from Flossenburg, they took us again with this cattle train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came to, to Ravensbruck-- the same grating with Arbeit, macht macht frei.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was very, very big campus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First, they took us to shower place, where they had-- they told us to strip everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The first day were looking for jewelry, which some women were hidden in their hair or gynecological place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Each woman was taken first to check hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One SS woman who checked my hair, she said, you bastard, you have too nice hair.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she shaved me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was shocked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was big loss for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And later, to gynecological examination, which was more difficult for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I was virgin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I can't understand how they could-- in private places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't argue-- not only-- we had to do what they want.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later, we, we were taken to shower with cold water, of course, with some kind of disinfectant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later, they gave us another dresses, also with stripe on the back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And nothing much-- nothing was proper, nothing warm.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
